4. Attribution (Enhanced Requirement)

Any use, distribution, or publication of the Model or Derivatives of the
Model MUST include clear and visible attribution to the original author.

The attribution MUST:

a. include the name “[TON NOM / PSEUDO]” as the original author;
b. mention that the Model is based on the original work by the author;
c. be displayed in a prominent location, such as:
   - a README file,
   - model card,
   - documentation,
   - user interface,
   - or public description of the Model.

Attribution MUST NOT be hidden solely in legal files or metadata.

